```plantuml
@startuml IBM_ios-mapkit-indoor-map

actor User
participant "iOS App" as iOS
participant "ViewController" as VC
participant "FloorplanOverlay" as FO
participant "FloorplanOverlayRenderer" as FOR
participant "CoordinateConverter" as CC
participant "VisibleMapRegionDelegate" as VMRD
participant "Node.js Backend" as Backend
participant "MongoDB" as DB

User -> iOS: Launch App
iOS -> VC: Initialize View
VC -> Backend: GET /api/mapdata
Backend -> DB: Query Map Data
DB --> Backend: Return Map Data
Backend --> VC: Return PDF Floorplan + Metadata

VC -> FO: Create Overlay(PDF)
FO -> CC: Setup Coordinate Conversion
VC -> FOR: Create Renderer(FO)
VC -> VMRD: Set Map Boundaries

User -> iOS: View Heatmap
iOS -> VC: Request Heatmap Data
VC -> Backend: GET /api/events
Backend -> DB: Query Trigger Events
DB --> Backend: Return Events
Backend --> VC: Return Event Data

VC -> FOR: Update Heatmap Overlay
FOR -> FO: Convert Coordinates(CC)
FO --> FOR: Converted Points
FOR -> iOS: Render Heatmap

User -> iOS: Interact with Map
iOS -> VMRD: Handle Camera Movement
VMRD -> iOS: Constrain Viewport

User -> iOS: Trigger Event
iOS -> Backend: POST /api/triggers
Backend -> DB: Store New Trigger
DB --> Backend: Confirm Storage
Backend --> iOS: Return Success

@enduml
```